Controls
========

Arrow Keys - Rotate the camera around the scene.
Q/A        - Change the value of the "S" parameter for the lorenz attractor.
W/S        - Change the value of the "B" parameter for the lorenz attractor.
E/D        - Change the value of the "R" parameter for the lorenz attractor.
,/.        - Change distance to the attractor.
1/2/3      - Change the color scheme of the attractor.
